			<h4>About Our Logo:</h4>
			<p>The Triskele, also known as the triple spiral, is the Celtic symbol for life. The symbol is a nod to Erik Hendricks’ Irish heritage and the foundation’s mission of improving the lives of those fighting HCL by raising funds to advance research into the disease. Additionally, the colors yellow and navy were Erik’s favorite colors. He was almost guaranteed to be dressed in one or both of those colors, or in head-to-toe yellow, earning him the nickname Yellow Bird.</p>
