			<p>For many years, Katie volunteered as a teacher for Citizen Schools, a non-profit that partners with public middle schools in low-income communities to provide an expanded learning day. Katie, along with two other friends, taught an apprenticeship program on entrepreneurship where the kids would learn firsthand what it takes to be an entrepreneur by starting their own business selling a product they would create.</p>
